{
  "stem": "22889.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where did your father go?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father went on the Russian side because Russia also got into-- Russia occupy half of the Poland and Germany, they had pact between each other and Germany occupy the other half.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my father went on the Russian side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wish he would've stayed, then maybe he would have been alive, who knows?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He followed the others, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he was lucky thing for him because when the German came to our town, right away they came in the-- with the list.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were searching for Jewish hostages and had my father name on the list.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know how they got that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, they came in-- and they-- they took right away Jewish hostages.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember they came over, the Germans, to our town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was just a youngster, and I wasn't afraid.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, my mother, she didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was don't go, don't go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were lived only about a half a block from our square, we had beautiful square around town.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember the German came in from all four side with the tanks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went, and-- and our square, in the center of the square was a-- they called it 'ratusz.' Was a-- what should I say?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's a city hall.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the German came in and, you know, to me was like a novelty to see a German.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't know who they were and so forth on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember I ran to the city hall with friend of mine in Israel, he lives in Israel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was a policeman.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was sitting drunk, and the German officer talked to him in Polish, we take over the town.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was demanding right away with the list.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
